The paper discusses deep learning-based approaches for image understanding, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The focus of the paper is on integrating knowledge and reasoning capabilities into these approaches, which is a key aspect of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses various methods for knowledge integration and reasoning, which are important topics in machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), and information retrieval (cs.IR). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
